title: Chermoula Chicken & Chickpea Tacos with Slivered Almonds & Garlic Aioli
description: Bursting with paprika, cumin and turmeric, our chermoula spice blend works wonderfully with tomato paste to create a saucy
base for the chickpeas. The salad and almonds add extra texture, and the tasty garlic aioli really makes the dish sing.
